Reasoning: The paper deals with visual tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also proposes a novel method for dynamic classifier selection, which involves machine learning techniques such as sparse representation (cs.LG) and potentially artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates its proposed method on challenging sequences, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and potentially computer security (cs.CR) if the sequences involve surveillance footage.
